name.value: Replicate Product Price and Discount from SAP S4HANA Cloud Public Edition to Shopify

customQueryOptions.value: $filter=Material eq '${property.product_sku}' and (ConditionType eq '${property.priceConditionType}' or ConditionType eq '${property.discountConditionType}')

wrapContent.value: { "query": "mutation updateProductVariants { productVariantsBulkUpdate(productId: \"${property.request_product_id}\", variants: [ { id: \"${property.request_variant_id}\", price: \"${property.sap_condition_rate_value}\" } ] ) { product { id } productVariants { id price } userErrors { field message } } } " }

{"query": "mutation { discountAutomaticBasicCreate(automaticBasicDiscount: {title: \"${property.title}\", startsAt: \"${property.sap_startsAt}\", endsAt: \"${property.sap_endsAt}\" , customerGets: {value: {percentage: ${property.percent_decimal_value} }, items: {products: {productsToAdd: [\"${property.request_product_id}\" ] } } } } )  { automaticDiscountNode { id automaticDiscount { ... on DiscountAutomaticBasic { startsAt endsAt minimumRequirement { ... on DiscountMinimumSubtotal { greaterThanOrEqualToSubtotal { amount currencyCode }  }  } customerGets { value { ... on DiscountAmount { amount { amount currencyCode } appliesOnEachItem }  } items { ... on AllDiscountItems { allItems  }  }  }  }  }  } userErrors { field code message  }  }  } " }
